How to Debug FluxPBX Issues
==============================

Dumping a core file
-------------------

Run:

    sysctl -w kernel.core_pattern=/tmp/core.%t_%e_s%s
    sysctl -w fs.suid_dumpable=1
    ulimit -c unlimited
    fluxpbx -core

Getting a backtrace from a core file
------------------------------------

Run:

    ./debian/scripts/backtrace-from-corefile /tmp/<name-of-corefile>
